            <title>[CASSANDRA-8579] sstablemetadata can&apos;t load org.apache.cassandra.tools.SSTableMetadataViewer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8579</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The sstablemetadata tool only works when running from the source tree. The classpath doesn&apos;t get set correctly when running on a deployed environment.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This bug looks to exist in 2.1 as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
